{"ID":"20251124203501-7tiku61","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20251124203501-7tiku61","title":"家中笔记","type":"doc","updated":"20260313072731"},"Children":[{"ID":"20251124203501-z8plebq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20251124203501-z8plebq","updated":"20260305074311"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"SPI"}]},{"ID":"20251124203516-iqil8qc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251124203516-iqil8qc","updated":"20251124203520"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20251124203520-g8sz3pg.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20251213195530-dtqpzv0","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20251213195530-dtqpzv0","updated":"20251213195547"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20251213195532-gjrz3op","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251213195532-gjrz3op","updated":"20251213195547"}}]},{"ID":"20251204074524-ii0cm34","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20251204074524-ii0cm34","updated":"20251217212522"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"spi时序"}]},{"ID":"20251204074454-dvnb5l0","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20251204074454-dvnb5l0","updated":"20251204074654"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20251204074457-z9xg1yi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251204074457-z9xg1yi","updated":"20251204074604"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"spi\t起始条件：ss从高电平切为低电平"}]},{"ID":"20251204074554-wpk9y7g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251204074554-wpk9y7g","updated":"20251204074619"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t终止条件：ss从低电平切为高电平"}]},{"ID":"20251204074637-9w03j46","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251204074637-9w03j46","updated":"20251204074637"}},{"ID":"20251204074638-fdg9u2c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251204074638-fdg9u2c","updated":"20251204074654"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"SCK 空闲状态为低电平"}]}]},{"ID":"20251204074620-jrdyahj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251204074620-jrdyahj","updated":"20251204075304"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20251204075304-pb4ru3a.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20251204075306-ks3z9tr","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20251204075306-ks3z9tr","updated":"20251204075409"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20251204075308-2fitvrd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251204075308-2fitvrd","updated":"20251204075409"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"流程：ss先下降沿 mosi移出数据 sck上升沿 mosi移入数据 sck下降沿 mosi再移出数据"}]}]},{"ID":"20251217212459-mkmysva","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20251217212459-mkmysva","updated":"20251217212833"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"W25Q64软件SPI"}]},{"ID":"20251217212646-pn530l6","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20251217212646-pn530l6","updated":"20251217212721"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20251217212648-fp4yjej","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251217212648-fp4yjej","updated":"20251217212721"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"软件spi的miso需要上拉稳定 不是有硬件控 是软件控 所以电平要稳定"}]}]},{"ID":"20251217212626-dos3xux","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20251217212626-dos3xux","updated":"20251217212751"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"void SPI_software_W_SS(uint8_t BitValue)\n{\n\tGPIO_WriteBit(GPIOB,GPIO_Pin_12, (BitAction)BitValue);\n}\n\nvoid SPI_software_W_SCK(uint8_t BitValue)\n{\n\tGPIO_WriteBit(GPIOB,GPIO_Pin_13, (BitAction)BitValue);\n}\n\nvoid SPI_software_W_MOSI(uint8_t BitValue)\n{\n\tGPIO_WriteBit(GPIOB,GPIO_Pin_15, (BitAction)BitValue);\n}\n\nuint8_t SPI_software_R_MISO(void)\n{\n\treturn GPIO_ReadInputDataBit(GPIOB, GPIO_Pin_14);\n}\n\n\n\n\n\nvoid SPI_software_Init(void)\n{\n\n  RCC_APB2PeriphClockCmd(RCC_APB2Periph_GPIOB, ENABLE);\n\t\n\tGPIO_InitTypeDef GPIO_InitStructure;\n \tGPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Mode = GPIO_Mode_Out_PP;\n\tGPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Speed = GPIO_Speed_50MHz;\n\tGPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Pin = GPIO_Pin_12 | GPIO_Pin_13 | GPIO_Pin_15; //  CC SCK MOSI\n \tGPIO_Init(GPIOB, \u0026GPIO_InitStructure);\n\n \tGPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Mode = GPIO_Mode_IPU;\n\tGPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Pin = GPIO_Pin_14;//MISO\n\tGPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Speed = GPIO_Speed_50MHz;\n\tGPIO_Init(GPIOB, \u0026GPIO_InitStructure);\n\t\n\tSPI_software_W_SS(1);\n\tSPI_software_W_SCK(0);\n\t\n}\n\n/***\nspi\t起始条件：ss从高电平切为低电平\n\n\t\t终止条件：ss从低电平切为高电平\n\n***/\nvoid SPI_software_Start(void)\n{\n\tSPI_software_W_SS(0);\n}\n\n\nvoid SPI_software_Stop(void)\n{\n\tSPI_software_W_SS(1);\n}\n\n//掩码方式\nuint8_t SPI_software_SwapByte_MaskOffCode(uint8_t ByteSend)\n{\n\t\n\tuint8_t ByteReceive = 0x00;\n\n\tfor(uint8_t i = 0; i \u003c8; i++)\n\t{\n\t\t\n\t\t/***\n\t\t\t前两步是主机将数据移出操作 从机怎么操作我们不关心\n\t\t***/\n\t\tSPI_software_W_MOSI(ByteSend \u0026 (0x80 \u003e\u003e i));//主机拿出数据\n\n\t\tSPI_software_W_SCK(1);//时钟上升沿\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t/***\n\t\t\t下面的操作是主机读取从机数据的操作\n\t\t***/\n\t\tif(SPI_software_R_MISO() == 1)//主机读取数据\n\t\t{\n\t\t\t/***\n\t\t\t\tByteReceive相当于 00000000 每一次位移都在对每一位进行改变\n\t\t\t\t比如从机数据为1100 1011\n\t\t\t\t第一次获取到的就是1 \n\t\t\t\t第二次要右移 读到的也是1 \n\t\t\t\t第三次读到的是0 就不将ByteReceive或1了\n\t\t\t***/\n\t\t\tByteReceive |= (0x80 \u003e\u003e i); //\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t}\n\t\t\n\t\tSPI_software_W_SCK(0);//时钟下降沿\n\t\t\n\t}\n\t\n\treturn ByteReceive;\n}\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20251217212500-9q1ube1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20251217212500-9q1ube1","updated":"20251217212833"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读取芯片id"}]},{"ID":"20251217212821-9ooxzrg","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20251217212821-9ooxzrg","updated":"20251217212826"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"void W25Q64_ReadID(uint8_t *MID, uint16_t *DID)//MID厂商 DID设备ID\n{\n\tSPI_software_Start();\n\tSPI_software_SwapByte_MaskOffCode(FLASH_JedecDeviceID);//给从机发信号 让从机回复设备信息\n\t*MID = SPI_software_SwapByte_MaskOffCode(0xFF);//主机随便抛一个字节用户数据交换，获取设备信息\n\t*DID = SPI_software_SwapByte_MaskOffCode(0xFF);//主机获取高8位数据\n\t*DID \u003c\u003c= 8;\n\t*DID |= SPI_software_SwapByte_MaskOffCode(0xFF);//主机获取低八位数据\n\tSPI_software_Stop();\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20251217212759-kxu4fzz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20251217212759-kxu4fzz","updated":"20260104065940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"NM25Q128硬件SPI"}]},{"ID":"20251217212853-wx27dw9","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20251217212853-wx27dw9","updated":"20251217212901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20251217212853-xn0rm3q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251217212853-xn0rm3q","updated":"20251217212901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"硬件配置下 miso要浮空 让硬件自己决定高低电平"}]}]},{"ID":"20251217212800-vw4cq54","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20251217212800-vw4cq54","updated":"20251217213031"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"void SPI_hardware_W_SS(uint8_t BitValue)\n{\n\tGPIO_WriteBit(GPIOB,GPIO_Pin_12, (BitAction)BitValue);\n}\n\n\n\nvoid SPI2_GPIO_Init(void)\n{\n    GPIO_InitTypeDef GPIO_InitStructure;\n\n    RCC_APB2PeriphClockCmd(RCC_APB2Periph_GPIOB | RCC_APB2Periph_AFIO, ENABLE);\n\n    /* CS: PB12 */\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Pin = GPIO_Pin_12;\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Mode = GPIO_Mode_Out_PP;\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Speed = GPIO_Speed_50MHz;\n    GPIO_Init(GPIOB, \u0026GPIO_InitStructure);\n    GPIO_SetBits(GPIOB, GPIO_Pin_12);\n\n    /* SCK: PB13, MOSI: PB15 */\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Pin = GPIO_Pin_13 | GPIO_Pin_15;\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Mode = GPIO_Mode_AF_PP;\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Speed = GPIO_Speed_50MHz;\n    GPIO_Init(GPIOB, \u0026GPIO_InitStructure);\n\n    /* MISO: PB14 */\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Pin = GPIO_Pin_14;\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Mode = GPIO_Mode_IN_FLOATING;//硬件配置下 miso要浮空 让硬件自己决定高低电平\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Speed = GPIO_Speed_50MHz;\n    GPIO_Init(GPIOB, \u0026GPIO_InitStructure);\n}\n\nvoid SPI_hardware_init(void)\n{\n\n    SPI_InitTypeDef SPI_InitStructure;\n\n    RCC_APB1PeriphClockCmd(RCC_APB1Periph_SPI2, ENABLE);\n\n    SPI_I2S_DeInit(SPI2);\n    SPI_StructInit(\u0026SPI_InitStructure);\n\n    SPI_InitStructure.SPI_Direction = SPI_Direction_2Lines_FullDuplex;//全双工\n    SPI_InitStructure.SPI_Mode = SPI_Mode_Master;//mcu为主机\n    SPI_InitStructure.SPI_DataSize = SPI_DataSize_8b;//每次8位\n    SPI_InitStructure.SPI_CPOL = SPI_CPOL_Low;//模式0\n    SPI_InitStructure.SPI_CPHA = SPI_CPHA_1Edge;//模式0\n    SPI_InitStructure.SPI_NSS = SPI_NSS_Soft;//cs片选位mcu控制 即自己控制片选引脚\n    SPI_InitStructure.SPI_BaudRatePrescaler = SPI_BaudRatePrescaler_256;//分频256\n    SPI_InitStructure.SPI_FirstBit = SPI_FirstBit_MSB;//高位先行\n    SPI_InitStructure.SPI_CRCPolynomial = 7;//crc\n\n    SPI_Init(SPI2, \u0026SPI_InitStructure);\n\n    SPI_Cmd(SPI2, ENABLE);\n\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20251217213045-l5zby3j","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20251217213045-l5zby3j","updated":"20260104065940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读取芯片id"}]},{"ID":"20251217213118-5vr8lh8","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20251217213118-5vr8lh8","updated":"20251217214006"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20251217213120-wyk652d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251217213120-wyk652d","updated":"20251217213206"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"硬件SPI flash必须等待数据接收 实际和软件spi的for循环8次是一个道理，等待整个周期"}]},{"ID":"20251217213212-fwdzcdf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251217213212-fwdzcdf","updated":"20251217214006"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最最关键的是初始化完所有配置后 需要发一次字节来清空dr保证芯片数据干净 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"background-color: var(--b3-card-error-background); color: var(--b3-card-error-color);"},"TextMarkType":"strong text","TextMarkTextContent":"这是导致一直读取不到id的原因"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"background-color: var(--b3-card-error-background); color: var(--b3-card-error-color);\"}"}]}]},{"ID":"20251217212800-aez8klt","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20251217212800-aez8klt","updated":"20251217213301"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"\n\nvoid NM25Q128_Init(void)\n{\n    SPI2_GPIO_Init();\n    SPI_hardware_init();\n\t\tspi_data_init();//这步最重要\n}\n\n\nvoid spi_data_init(void)\n{\n\t//给spi先发一个无效字节 清空DR 保证初始化\n    SPI_hardware_W_SS(0);              // 片选拉低\n    uint8_t val = NM25Q128_SPI2_read_write_byte(0xFF);  // 发一个 FF，读一字节\n    SPI_hardware_W_SS(1);\n   \n}\n\n\n\n\nuint8_t NM25Q128_SPI2_read_write_byte(uint8_t tx_data)\n{\n    while (SPI_I2S_GetFlagStatus(SPI2, SPI_I2S_FLAG_TXE) == RESET); //等发送缓冲空\n    SPI_I2S_SendData(SPI2, tx_data);\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  // 写入要发送的数据\n    while (SPI_I2S_GetFlagStatus(SPI2, SPI_I2S_FLAG_RXNE) == RESET);// 等接收完成\n    return (uint8_t)SPI_I2S_ReceiveData(SPI2);\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t// 返回本次收到的字节\n}\n\n\n\nvoid NM25Q128_ReadID(uint8_t *MID, uint16_t *DID, uint16_t order)\n{\n    uint16_t deviceid;\n\t\n    SPI_hardware_W_SS(0);\n\t\n\t\tif(order == NM25Q128_CMD_READ_MANUFACTURER_ID)//0x90\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tNM25Q128_SPI2_read_write_byte(0x90); // 0x90\n\t\t\tNM25Q128_SPI2_read_write_byte(0x00);\n\t\t\tNM25Q128_SPI2_read_write_byte(0x00);\n\t\t\tNM25Q128_SPI2_read_write_byte(0x00);\n\t\t\t*DID = NM25Q128_SPI2_read_write_byte(0xFF) \u003c\u003c 8;\n\t\t\t*DID |= NM25Q128_SPI2_read_write_byte(0xFF);\n\t\t}\n\t\telse if(order == NM25Q128_CMD_READ_JEDEC_ID)//0x9F\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tNM25Q128_SPI2_read_write_byte(0x9F);//给从机发信号 让从机回复设备信息\n\t\t\t*MID = NM25Q128_SPI2_read_write_byte(0xFF);//主机随便抛一个字节用户数据交换，获取设备信息\n\t\t\t*DID = NM25Q128_SPI2_read_write_byte(0xFF);//主机获取高8位数据\n\t\t\t*DID \u003c\u003c= 8;\n\t\t\t*DID |= NM25Q128_SPI2_read_write_byte(0xFF);//主机获取低八位数据\n\t\t\n\t\t}\n\n    SPI_hardware_W_SS(1);\n}\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20251217212800-dq6h5n7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251217212800-dq6h5n7","updated":"20251217212800"}},{"ID":"20251215220456-totfjbi","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220456-totfjbi","updated":"20260305074013"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为什么韦东山的板子oled模拟i2c用不了"}]},{"ID":"20260104065945-2d8hm8n","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260104065945-2d8hm8n","updated":"20260104070529"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20260104065946-ekkel4p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260104065946-ekkel4p","updated":"20260104070529"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"具体原因还没找到 但是换两个引脚 不用自带的oled硬件脚就没问题 猜测是硬件电路中上拉电阻的影响"}]}]},{"ID":"20251215220456-ybs5c4m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220456-ybs5c4m","updated":"20251215220456"}},{"ID":"20251215220456-pxgv8jq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220456-pxgv8jq","updated":"20260305074619"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ADC"}]},{"ID":"20260305074016-1hz9vhv","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260305074016-1hz9vhv","updated":"20260305074152"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20260305074041-g82t6lp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305074041-g82t6lp","updated":"20260305074055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"传感器引脚为AO是adc输入"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305074602-d50xm25","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305074602-d50xm25","updated":"20260305074619"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"扫描模式"}]},{"ID":"20260305074602-7ym0527","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260305074602-7ym0527","updated":"20260305074619"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305074619-wip2upx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305074619-wip2upx","updated":"20260305074619"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ADC 扫描模式（Scan Mode）：指 ADC 在一次启动后，按你预先配置的“通道序列”（rank 顺序）自动依次对多个通道进行转换。也就是硬件会从序列的第 1 个通道开始，逐个通道采样并转换，直到序列结束（End of Sequence，EOS）。常用于多通道采集，通常配合 DMA 把每个通道的结果按顺序搬到内存数组。"}]},{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"}]},{"ID":"20260305074540-isnvkl2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305074540-isnvkl2","updated":"20260305074636"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"单次扫描"}]},{"ID":"20260305074550-a31lwg1","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260305074550-a31lwg1","updated":"20260305074636"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20260305074630-iauvsn0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305074630-iauvsn0","updated":"20260305074636"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"单次扫描（Single Scan）：启动一次，只把整个通道序列转换一遍就停止。转换完成会产生 EOS 标志（或触发中断/事件）。适合“按需测一次”的场景，例如偶尔读取多路电压快照。常见搭配：扫描模式=开，连续转换=关，DMA=普通模式（一次搬运）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305074551-nrk6ytl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305074551-nrk6ytl","updated":"20260305074654"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"连续扫描"}]},{"ID":"20260305074647-6ls2tk4","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260305074647-6ls2tk4","updated":"20260305074654"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20260305074647-i8l0s7m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305074647-i8l0s7m","updated":"20260305074654"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"连续扫描（Continuous Scan）：完成一遍序列后，自动从序列的第一个通道再次开始，周而复始，直到你停止。适合持续采样多路通道。常见搭配：扫描模式=开，连续转换=开，DMA=循环模式（环形缓冲区重复填充）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305075922-f9dz1lc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305075922-f9dz1lc","updated":"20260305080112"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是否要用dma来扫描"}]},{"ID":"20260305074555-nvq5ghx","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260305074555-nvq5ghx","updated":"20260305075938"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20260305075938-m6ejgv2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305075938-m6ejgv2","updated":"20260305075938"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"经验法则（面向常见 Cortex‑M MCU）"}]},{"ID":"20260305075938-ifdvm2e","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260305075938-ifdvm2e","updated":"20260305075938"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305075938-akha7ef","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260305075938-akha7ef","updated":"20260305075938"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305075938-qyuqec9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305075938-qyuqec9","updated":"20260305075938"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 个通道：≤20 kS/s 多数可不用 DMA；≥50 kS/s 建议 DMA。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305075938-3i53cy4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260305075938-3i53cy4","updated":"20260305075938"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305075938-orkjoha","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305075938-orkjoha","updated":"20260305075938"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2–3 个通道：若总事件率≥30–50 k 次/秒，建议 DMA；每通道≥10 kS/s 基本用 DMA。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305075938-i17ksw3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260305075938-i17ksw3","updated":"20260305075938"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305075938-m0hsiy8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305075938-m0hsiy8","updated":"20260305075938"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"≥4 个通道：通常用 DMA；除非每通道 ≤1 kS/s 且 CPU 很空闲。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305075938-9fzs1r4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260305075938-9fzs1r4","updated":"20260305075938"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305075938-670zwqw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305075938-670zwqw","updated":"20260305075938"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"连续扫描：为了防止覆盖/乱序/抖动，基本从 2 通道起就优先 DMA（配循环或双缓冲）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305075938-u7ysgq7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260305075938-u7ysgq7","updated":"20260305075938"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305075938-lnu9006","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305075938-lnu9006","updated":"20260305075938"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"精密定时采样：用“定时器触发 + DMA”（即使通道少、速率不高），获得稳准等间隔。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305074540-165ry64","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305074540-165ry64","updated":"20260305080350"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注入组\u0026规则组"}]},{"ID":"20260305080341-h8rsoon","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305080341-h8rsoon","updated":"20260305080350"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"定义"}]},{"ID":"20260305080114-3duzezp","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260305080114-3duzezp","updated":"20260305080311"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305080307-vk8d947","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305080307-vk8d947","updated":"20260305080307"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"规则组（Regular）：通用采样通道序列，用于常规、多通道轮询采集。"}]},{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20260305080307-7iboi68","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305080307-7iboi68","updated":"20260305080311"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注入组（Injected）：为“关键时刻采样”设计的独立序列，常用定时器/PWM 事件在特定相位触发，适合电机相电流等对时序极敏的量。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305080334-foes3fx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305080334-foes3fx","updated":"20260306073634"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用规则"}]},{"ID":"20260305080352-hgjejah","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260305080352-hgjejah","updated":"20260305080406"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305080353-chxkgj3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305080353-chxkgj3","updated":"20260305080353"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"规则组：支持软件触发、定时器触发，也可连续转换；若开连续，首次触发后会自由连续，后续触发可能不再生效（取决于芯片）。"}]},{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20260305080353-cvtvyw1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305080353-cvtvyw1","updated":"20260305080406"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注入组：通常由外部事件或软件单次触发；每次触发就插入执行一次注入序列，强锁定到事件时刻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305080357-zaqlnv1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305080357-zaqlnv1","updated":"20260306073713"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"DMA工作条件"}]},{"ID":"20260306073636-dcq8gc5","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260306073636-dcq8gc5","updated":"20260306073713"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20260306073637-dl5umo3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260306073637-dl5umo3","updated":"20260306073646"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.传输计数器大于0"}]},{"ID":"20260306073648-k9wweiw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260306073648-k9wweiw","updated":"20260306073657"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.触发源有触发信号"}]},{"ID":"20260306073706-602hwef","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260306073706-602hwef","updated":"20260306073713"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.DMA使能"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305080102-lu1kh70","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305080102-lu1kh70","updated":"20260305080102"}},{"ID":"20260305080102-tarq7qv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305080102-tarq7qv","updated":"20260305080102"}},{"ID":"20260305074540-0xfb5tc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305074540-0xfb5tc","updated":"20260305074540"}},{"ID":"20260305074152-8p2l78e","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305074152-8p2l78e","updated":"20260305074258"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"光敏传感器"}]},{"ID":"20251215220456-fxofrbv","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220456-fxofrbv","updated":"20260305074130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"#include \"stm32f10x.h\"\n#include \"Photoresistor.h\"\n\nvoid AD_Init(void)\n{\n    GPIO_InitTypeDef GPIO_InitStructure;\n\n    RCC_APB2PeriphClockCmd(RCC_APB2Periph_GPIOB | RCC_APB2Periph_GPIOA | RCC_APB2Periph_ADC1, ENABLE);\n\tRCC_ADCCLKConfig(RCC_PCLK2_Div6);//ADC时钟分频  72M/6 = 12MHZ\n\t\n\t\n    /* CS: PA3 */\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Pin = GPIO_Pin_3 | GPIO_Pin_2 | GPIO_Pin_1;\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Mode = GPIO_Mode_AIN;//模拟输入 不影响adc\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Speed = GPIO_Speed_50MHz;\n    GPIO_Init(GPIOA, \u0026GPIO_InitStructure);\n    \n\t//ADC_RegularChannelConfig(ADC1, ADC_Channel_3, 1,ADC_SampleTime_55Cycles5);// 单通道 选择通道0 转换列表菜单中一共16个位置 这里选第一个 采样时间选55.5个cycle\n\n\tADC_InitTypeDef ADC_InitStructure;\n\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_ContinuousConvMode = DISABLE;//单次扫描\n\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_DataAlign = ADC_DataAlign_Right;//右对齐\n\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_ExternalTrigConv = ADC_ExternalTrigConv_None;//软件触发 无触发源\n\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_Mode = ADC_Mode_Independent;//独立模式 adc1和adc2各负责各自的\n\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_NbrOfChannel = 1;//可选范围1-16 即菜单列表长度 因为这里是非扫描 所以没有用 写一个就可以\n\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_ScanConvMode = DISABLE;//非扫描模式\n\tADC_Init(ADC1, \u0026ADC_InitStructure);\n\t\n\tADC_Cmd(ADC1, ENABLE);//adc上电\n\t\n\tADC_ResetCalibration(ADC1);//复位校准\n\twhile (ADC_GetResetCalibrationStatus(ADC1) == SET);//返回复位校准的状态 RESET就说明复位校准完成\n\tADC_StartCalibration(ADC1);//开始校准\n\twhile ( ADC_GetCalibrationStatus(ADC1) == SET);//校准完成\n\t\t\n}\n\nuint16_t AD_GetValue(uint8_t ADC_Channel)\n{\n\tADC_RegularChannelConfig(ADC1, ADC_Channel, 1,ADC_SampleTime_55Cycles5);// \n\tADC_SoftwareStartConvCmd(ADC1, ENABLE);\n\twhile(ADC_GetFlagStatus(ADC1, ADC_FLAG_EOC) == RESET);//转换时间 72mhz/6分频 = 12mhz  采样总时间为 1 / 12mhz * 68（55.5个采样周期 + 12.5个固定转换周期） = 5.6微秒\t\n\treturn ADC_GetConversionValue(ADC1);\n\n}\n\n\nfloat adc_calculate(uint16_t adc_value)\n{\n\t\n\tfloat adc_voltage;\n\tadc_voltage = (float)adc_value / 4095 * 3.3;\n\treturn adc_voltage;\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20251215220456-rsr6pev","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220456-rsr6pev","updated":"20251215220456"}},{"ID":"20251215220456-23y7gaw","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220456-23y7gaw","updated":"20260310082703"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"DMA+ADC"}]},{"ID":"20260310082419-douz7u6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260310082419-douz7u6","updated":"20260310082703"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"单次扫描 DMA单次转运不循环"}]},{"ID":"20260310082542-nkclepc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260310082542-nkclepc","updated":"20260310082703"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意事项"}]},{"ID":"20260310082550-djkquq9","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260310082550-djkquq9","updated":"20260310082703"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20260310082552-auxgx6e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260310082552-auxgx6e","updated":"20260310082632"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.ADC多条通道转换顺序要按照RANK参数来 就是这里的3"}]},{"ID":"20260310082633-txbjlxy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260310082633-txbjlxy","updated":"20260310082703"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.ADC通道和引脚注意要对齐，按照手册PA2就是对应ADC_Channel_2"}]},{"ID":"20260310082619-zsv6z1h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260310082619-zsv6z1h","updated":"20260310082619"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ADC_RegularChannelConfig(ADC1, ADC_Channel_2, 3,ADC_SampleTime_55Cycles5);"}]}]},{"ID":"20260310082543-lsmr4dp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260310082543-lsmr4dp","updated":"20260310082543"}},{"ID":"20251215220456-joivy9g","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220456-joivy9g","updated":"20260310082322"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"DMA配置文件"}]},{"ID":"20260310082238-sfe5pno","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20260310082238-sfe5pno","updated":"20260310082305"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"void My_DMA_init(void)\n{\n\t\n\tRCC_AHBPeriphClockCmd(RCC_AHBPeriph_DMA1, ENABLE);\n\tDMA_InitTypeDef DMA_InitStructure;\n\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_PeripheralBaseAddr = (uint32_t)\u0026ADC1-\u003eDR;//外设站点地址\n\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_PeripheralDataSize = DMA_PeripheralDataSize_HalfWord;//传输的数据大小 字节 半字 字\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_PeripheralInc = DMA_PeripheralInc_Disable;//地址不自增 注意如果是数组就要自增 但是硬件地址不要自增\n\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_MemoryBaseAddr = (uint32_t)\u0026ADC_paramater.ADC_list;//存储器站点\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_MemoryDataSize = DMA_MemoryDataSize_HalfWord;//数据大小\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_MemoryInc = DMA_MemoryInc_Enable;//地址自增\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_DIR = DMA_DIR_PeripheralSRC;//传输方向 DMA_DIR_PeripheralSRC:外设-\u003e存储器  or  DMA_DIR_PeripheralDST:存储器-\u003e外设   \n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_Priority = DMA_Priority_Medium;\t//优先级\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_BufferSize = ADC_LIST_LENGTH;//数组大小\n\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_M2M = DMA_M2M_Disable;//enable:软件触发 disable:硬件触发\n\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_Mode = DMA_Mode_Normal;//dma转运模式 是否自动重装 circular：自动重装 normal:不重装\n\n\tDMA_Init(DMA1_Channel1, \u0026DMA_InitStructure);\n\t\n\tDMA_Cmd(DMA1_Channel1, ENABLE);\n\n\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20251215220456-gzxpi5m","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220456-gzxpi5m","updated":"20260310082326"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ADC配置"}]},{"ID":"20251215220457-dxbu9x6","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-dxbu9x6","updated":"20260310082350"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"void AD_Init(void)\n{\n    GPIO_InitTypeDef GPIO_InitStructure;\n\n    RCC_APB2PeriphClockCmd(RCC_APB2Periph_GPIOB | RCC_APB2Periph_GPIOA | RCC_APB2Periph_ADC1, ENABLE);\n\t\tRCC_ADCCLKConfig(RCC_PCLK2_Div6);//ADC时钟分频  72M/6 = 12MHZ\n\t\n\t\n    /* CS: PA3 */\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Pin = GPIO_Pin_3 | GPIO_Pin_2 | GPIO_Pin_1;\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Mode = GPIO_Mode_AIN;//模拟输入 不影响adc\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Speed = GPIO_Speed_50MHz;\n    GPIO_Init(GPIOA, \u0026GPIO_InitStructure);\n    \n\t\t//注意采集转换的顺序就是按照 rank这个参数 这里就是PA3第一个采集\n\t\tADC_RegularChannelConfig(ADC1, ADC_Channel_1, 2,ADC_SampleTime_55Cycles5);// 单通道 选择通道0 转换列表菜单中一共16个位置 这里选第一个 采样时间选55.5个cycle\n\t\tADC_RegularChannelConfig(ADC1, ADC_Channel_2, 3,ADC_SampleTime_55Cycles5);\t\n\t\tADC_RegularChannelConfig(ADC1, ADC_Channel_3, 1,ADC_SampleTime_55Cycles5);\n\n\t\tADC_InitTypeDef ADC_InitStructure;\n\t\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_ContinuousConvMode = DISABLE;//单次扫描\n\t\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_DataAlign = ADC_DataAlign_Right;//右对齐\n\t\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_ExternalTrigConv = ADC_ExternalTrigConv_None;//软件触发 无触发源\n\t\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_Mode = ADC_Mode_Independent;//独立模式 adc1和adc2各负责各自的\n\t\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_NbrOfChannel = ADC_LIST_LENGTH;//可选范围1-16 即菜单列表长度 因为这里是非扫描 所以没有用 写一个就可以\n\t\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_ScanConvMode = ENABLE;//扫描模式\n\t\tADC_Init(ADC1, \u0026ADC_InitStructure);\n\t\t\n\t\tADC_Cmd(ADC1, ENABLE);//adc上电\n\t\tADC_DMACmd(ADC1, ENABLE);//Enables or disables the specified ADC DMA request.\n\t\tADC_ResetCalibration(ADC1);//复位校准\n\t\twhile (ADC_GetResetCalibrationStatus(ADC1) == SET);//返回复位校准的状态 RESET就说明复位校准完成\n\t\tADC_StartCalibration(ADC1);//开始校准\n\t\twhile ( ADC_GetCalibrationStatus(ADC1) == SET);//校准完成\n\t\t\n}\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20251215220457-xn1ldx2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-xn1ldx2","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-uvoymqm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-uvoymqm","updated":"20260310082529"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"转换逻辑"}]},{"ID":"20251215220457-mxeo59k","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-mxeo59k","updated":"20260310082505"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"void AD_GetValue(void)\n{\n\n\tDMA_Cmd(DMA1_Channel1, DISABLE);\n\tDMA_SetCurrDataCounter(DMA1_Channel1, ADC_LIST_LENGTH);\n\tDMA_Cmd(DMA1_Channel1, ENABLE);\n\t//因为是单次转运 所以要软件先触发一次\n\tADC_SoftwareStartConvCmd(ADC1, ENABLE);\n\t\n\twhile(DMA_GetFlagStatus(DMA1_FLAG_TC1) == RESET);\n\tDMA_ClearFlag(DMA1_FLAG_TC1);\n\t\n}\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20251215220457-x0f0j82","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-x0f0j82","updated":"20260313072353"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"主函数逻辑"}]},{"ID":"20260310082530-fndmhf5","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20260310082530-fndmhf5","updated":"20260310082531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"\t\t//光敏电阻\n\t\tAD_GetValue();\n\t\tad_value_photo_resistor = ADC_paramater.ADC_list[0];\n\t\tVoltage_photo_resistor = adc_calculate(ad_value_photo_resistor);\n\t\t\n\t\t//霍尔\n\t\tad_value_hall = ADC_paramater.ADC_list[2];\n\t\tVoltage_hall = adc_calculate(ad_value_hall);\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t//热敏电阻\n\t\tad_value_hot_resistor =  ADC_paramater.ADC_list[1];\n\t\tVoltage_hot_resistor = adc_calculate(ad_value_hot_resistor);\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20251215220457-0u8t1vt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-0u8t1vt","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-bgumgws","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-bgumgws","updated":"20260313072554"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"DMA循环搬运ADC"}]},{"ID":"20260313072435-spjh75p","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20260313072435-spjh75p","updated":"20260313072453"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"defined(DMA_CONTINUOUS)\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20260313072418-ilwtg7c","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260313072418-ilwtg7c","updated":"20260313072554"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ADC配置"}]},{"ID":"20260313072356-yoqv5yz","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20260313072356-yoqv5yz","updated":"20260313072535"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"#include \"includes.h\"\n#include \"Photoresistor.h\"\nADC_paramater_t ADC_paramater;\nvoid AD_Init(void)\n{\n    GPIO_InitTypeDef GPIO_InitStructure;\n\n    RCC_APB2PeriphClockCmd(RCC_APB2Periph_GPIOB | RCC_APB2Periph_GPIOA | RCC_APB2Periph_ADC1, ENABLE);\n\t\tRCC_ADCCLKConfig(RCC_PCLK2_Div6);//ADC时钟分频  72M/6 = 12MHZ\n\t\n\t\n    /* CS: PA3 */\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Pin = GPIO_Pin_3 | GPIO_Pin_2 | GPIO_Pin_1;\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Mode = GPIO_Mode_AIN;//模拟输入 不影响adc\n    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Speed = GPIO_Speed_50MHz;\n    GPIO_Init(GPIOA, \u0026GPIO_InitStructure);\n    \n\t\t//注意采集转换的顺序就是按照 rank这个参数 这里就是PA3第一个采集\n\t\tADC_RegularChannelConfig(ADC1, ADC_Channel_1, 2,ADC_SampleTime_55Cycles5);// 单通道 选择通道0 转换列表菜单中一共16个位置 这里选第一个 采样时间选55.5个cycle\n\t\tADC_RegularChannelConfig(ADC1, ADC_Channel_2, 3,ADC_SampleTime_55Cycles5);\t\n\t\tADC_RegularChannelConfig(ADC1, ADC_Channel_3, 1,ADC_SampleTime_55Cycles5);\n\n\t\tADC_InitTypeDef ADC_InitStructure;\n\t\t#if defined(DMA_ONCE)\n\t\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_ContinuousConvMode = DISABLE;//单次扫描\n\t\t#elif defined(DMA_CONTINUOUS)\n\t\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_ContinuousConvMode = ENABLE;//连续扫描\t\t\n\t\t#endif\n\t\t\n\t\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_DataAlign = ADC_DataAlign_Right;//右对齐\n\t\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_ExternalTrigConv = ADC_ExternalTrigConv_None;//软件触发 无触发源\n\t\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_Mode = ADC_Mode_Independent;//独立模式 adc1和adc2各负责各自的\n\t\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_NbrOfChannel = ADC_LIST_LENGTH;//可选范围1-16 即菜单列表长度 因为这里是非扫描 所以没有用 写一个就可以\n\t\tADC_InitStructure.ADC_ScanConvMode = ENABLE;//扫描模式\n\t\tADC_Init(ADC1, \u0026ADC_InitStructure);\n\t\t\n\t\tADC_Cmd(ADC1, ENABLE);//adc上电\n\t\tADC_DMACmd(ADC1, ENABLE);//Enables or disables the specified ADC DMA request.\n\t\tADC_ResetCalibration(ADC1);//复位校准\n\t\twhile (ADC_GetResetCalibrationStatus(ADC1) == SET);//返回复位校准的状态 RESET就说明复位校准完成\n\t\tADC_StartCalibration(ADC1);//开始校准\n\t\twhile ( ADC_GetCalibrationStatus(ADC1) == SET);//校准完成\n\t\t\n\t\t//如果是adc自动硬件转换就要在初始化的时候就cmd启动\n\t\t#ifdef DMA_CONTINUOUS\n\t\tADC_SoftwareStartConvCmd(ADC1, ENABLE);\t\n\t\t#endif\t\t\n\t\t\n}\n\nfloat adc_calculate(uint16_t adc_value)\n{\n\t\n\tfloat adc_voltage;\n\tadc_voltage = (float)adc_value / 4095 * 3.3;\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\treturn adc_voltage;\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20251215220457-k26tm04","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-k26tm04","updated":"20260313072641"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"DMA配置"}]},{"ID":"20251215220457-co2elas","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-co2elas","updated":"20260313072609"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"#include \"includes.h\"\n#include \"My_DMA.h\"\n\nDMA_Parameter_t DMA_Parameter;\n\n\n\nvoid My_DMA_init(void)\n{\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\tRCC_AHBPeriphClockCmd(RCC_AHBPeriph_DMA1, ENABLE);\n\n\tDMA_InitTypeDef DMA_InitStructure;\n\n\n\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_PeripheralBaseAddr = (uint32_t)\u0026ADC1-\u003eDR;//外设站点地址\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_PeripheralDataSize = DMA_PeripheralDataSize_HalfWord;//传输的数据大小 字节 半字 字\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_PeripheralInc = DMA_PeripheralInc_Disable;//地址自增\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_MemoryBaseAddr = (uint32_t)\u0026ADC_paramater.ADC_list;//存储器站点\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_MemoryDataSize = DMA_MemoryDataSize_HalfWord;//数据大小\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_MemoryInc = DMA_MemoryInc_Enable;//地址自增\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_DIR = DMA_DIR_PeripheralSRC;//传输方向 DMA_DIR_PeripheralSRC:外设-\u003e存储器  or  DMA_DIR_PeripheralDST:存储器-\u003e外设   \n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_Priority = DMA_Priority_Medium;\t//优先级\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_BufferSize = ADC_LIST_LENGTH;//数组大小\n\n\t#if defined(DMA_ONCE)\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_Mode = DMA_Mode_Normal;//dma转运模式 是否自动重装 circular：自动重装 normal:不重装\n\t#elif defined(DMA_CONTINUOUS)\n\tDMA_InitStructure.DMA_Mode = DMA_Mode_Circular;//dma转运模式 是否自动重装 circular：自动重装 normal:不重装\n\t#endif\n\t\n\n\tDMA_Init(DMA1_Channel1, \u0026DMA_InitStructure);\n\t\n\tDMA_Cmd(DMA1_Channel1, ENABLE);\n\n\n}\n\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20251215220457-jvhu4j2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-jvhu4j2","updated":"20260313072731"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"主程序"}]},{"ID":"20260313072643-vra4idk","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20260313072643-vra4idk","updated":"20260313072731"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"#include \"stm32f10x.h\"                  // Device header\n\n#include \"includes.h\"\n\nuint16_t ad_value_photo_resistor;\nuint16_t ad_value_hot_resistor;\nuint16_t ad_value_hall;\nfloat Voltage_photo_resistor;\nfloat Voltage_hot_resistor;\nfloat Voltage_hall;\n\nuint8_t aaa = 0;\nint main(void)\n{\naaa = sizeof(ADC_paramater.ADC_list);\n\t/*OLED初始化*/\n\tOLED_Init();\n\n\n\t\n\tAD_Init();\n\tMy_DMA_init();\n\t\n\t\n\tOLED_ShowString(1, 1, \"AD_VALUE:\", OLED_6X8);\n\tOLED_ShowString(1, 9, \"Voltage: .  V\", OLED_6X8);\n\t\n\tOLED_ShowString(1, 17, \"AD_VALUE:\", OLED_6X8);\n\tOLED_ShowString(1, 26, \"Voltage: .  V\", OLED_6X8);\t\n\t\n\tOLED_ShowString(1, 35, \"AD_VALUE:\", OLED_6X8);\n\tOLED_ShowString(1, 44, \"Voltage: .  V\", OLED_6X8);\n\t\n\twhile(1)\n\t{\n\t\t//此处只需要初始化就可以 不需要再手动获取\n\t\t#ifdef DMA_ONCE\n\t\tAD_GetValue();\n\t\t#endif\n\t\t\n\t\t//光敏电阻\n\t\tad_value_photo_resistor = ADC_paramater.ADC_list[0];\n\t\tVoltage_photo_resistor = adc_calculate(ad_value_photo_resistor);\n\t\t\n\t\t//霍尔\n\t\tad_value_hall = ADC_paramater.ADC_list[2];\n\t\tVoltage_hall = adc_calculate(ad_value_hall);\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t//热敏电阻\n\t\tad_value_hot_resistor =  ADC_paramater.ADC_list[1];\n\t\tVoltage_hot_resistor = adc_calculate(ad_value_hot_resistor);\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tOLED_ShowNum(54,1,ad_value_photo_resistor, 4,OLED_6X8);\n\t\t\t\n\t\tOLED_ShowNum(48,9,Voltage_photo_resistor, 1,OLED_6X8);\n\t\t\t\n\t\tOLED_ShowNum(60,9,(uint16_t)(Voltage_photo_resistor * 100) % 100, 2,OLED_6X8);\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tOLED_ShowNum(54,17,ad_value_hall, 4,OLED_6X8);\n\t\t\t\n\t\tOLED_ShowNum(48,26,Voltage_hall, 1,OLED_6X8);\n\t\t\t\n\t\tOLED_ShowNum(60,26,(uint16_t)(Voltage_hall * 100) % 100, 2,OLED_6X8);\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tOLED_ShowNum(54,35,ad_value_hot_resistor, 4,OLED_6X8);\n\t\t\t\n\t\tOLED_ShowNum(48,44,Voltage_hot_resistor, 1,OLED_6X8);\n\t\t\t\n\t\tOLED_ShowNum(60,44,(uint16_t)(Voltage_hot_resistor * 100) % 100, 2,OLED_6X8);\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDelay_ms(100);\n\t\t\n\t\tOLED_Update();\n\t\n\t}\n\t\n}\n\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20251215220457-efelpns","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-efelpns","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-a9ue044","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-a9ue044","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-n2d6z1r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-n2d6z1r","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-833mctx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-833mctx","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-7gvz1g7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-7gvz1g7","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-7bucutj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-7bucutj","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-mwrel5g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-mwrel5g","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-0yua4qk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-0yua4qk","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-5sfi479","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-5sfi479","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-jgd7p14","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-jgd7p14","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-j0eqtty","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-j0eqtty","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-yz2l1ja","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-yz2l1ja","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-c8oqj6b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-c8oqj6b","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-h7y85li","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-h7y85li","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-53x32r0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-53x32r0","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-tp87nke","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-tp87nke","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-nm8dvxc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-nm8dvxc","updated":"20251215220457"}},{"ID":"20251215220457-xh57n7y","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220457-xh57n7y","updated":"20260104064624"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一些问题"}]},{"ID":"20251215220503-lf1y9s7","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220503-lf1y9s7","updated":"20260104064624"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"打断点被优化"}]},{"ID":"20251215220513-rao2108","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20251215220513-rao2108","updated":"20251215220516"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dW5kZWZpbmVk"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int main(void)\n{\n    volatile int flag = 0;\n\n    SystemCoreClockUpdate();\n    flag = 1;   // ← 在这里打断点\n\n    while (1);\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20251215220522-nqld3s6","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20251215220522-nqld3s6","updated":"20251215220532"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20251215220524-iv4trkq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20251215220524-iv4trkq","updated":"20251215220532"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"通过volatile 就不会优化代码"}]}]},{"ID":"20260104064624-v05p51n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260104064624-v05p51n","updated":"20260104064624"}}]}